Package ORM

Class Cache

java.lang.Object
ORM.Cache
public class Cache
extends java.lang.Object

Class Cache

Own class for cache objects so instances of filled custom database objects can be cached. Expands the simple entity cache in Manager, which only stores the empty entity objects of custom classes for runtime efficiency.
